"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-comment-podcasts-team-gb-s-gold-medal-rush-begins-at-paris-2024-olympics-b1173579.html\", \"text\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies. Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search. See our privacy policy for more information.  Comment|Podcasts  Listen here on your chosen podcast platform.  Great Britain's gold rush begins with our victory of Paris 2024 as Ros Canter, Tom McEwen and Laura Collett triumph in equestrian team eventing at the Ch\\u00e2teau de Versailles.  Tom Daley earlier scooped a remarkable fifth Olympic diving medal as he took silver alongside Noah Williams in men's synchronised 10m platform final.  It came after Adam Peaty narrowly missed out on the top podium spot to retain his title by a cruel 0.02 seconds in the men's 100m breaststroke, and settled for joint silver.  Kimberley Woods also took bronze in the women's individual kayak.  For more on Monday's Paris successes, The Standard podcast is joined by reporter Robert Dex, who's been covering developments.  In part two, in her first major speech as chancellor, Rachel Reeves identifies a \\u00a320 billion black hole in government spending as she seeks to pin the blame for future tax rises on Tory profligacy.  Reeves's spending cut targets include more empty public buildings sell-offs, plus slashing government investment on some road-building projects - and there is concerns about the future of central London's High Speed 2 rail link.  We have policy analysis, plus the latest on the Conservative leadership race, with Evening Standard political editor, Nicholas Cecil.  MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\"}"